5.2 Find File At Point
======================

Find File At Point, also known generally as "ffap", is an intelligent
system for opening files, and URLs.

   The following expression will make Ido guess the context:

     (setq ido-use-filename-at-point 'guess)

   You can disable URL ffap support by toggling `ido-use-url-at-point'.

 -- User Option: ido-use-url-at-point
     If the value of this user option is non-`nil', Ido will look for a
     URL at point.  If found, call `find-file-at-point' to visit it.


